---
title: Spiced Chicken & Roasted Carrot Bowls with Tangy Hummus Sauce & Apricot-Almond Gremolata
description: This filling dinner bowl is bursting with warm, sunshiny flavors! Carrots are roasted to bring out their natural sweetness, while lemon juice and yogurt star in a hummus sauce that adds creaminess to every bite. Our chefs also dreamed up a fruity twist on herby gremolata that adds crunch and citrusy tang to Turkish-spiced chicken and rice. So pile your bowls high!
